items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great purchase
items.body: Great dress. I put a broach on one side so the shoulder would stay where I wanted it to all night. Very flattering. Good price. Would recommend. Read more
items.author: Nicholas Hull

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft and luxurious off the shoulder dress. Very flattering!
items.body: This dress came packaged and folded nicely without any intrusive odor. The material is soft and luxurious with a nice thickness to it. I love the off the shoulder style. This dress is so comfy, I will be able to wear this dress around the house or out to winter parties. I appreciate the versatility. Overall I highly recommend adding this to your wardrobe. Read more
items.author: Kaity Millen-Giles

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Los volvería a comprar en varios colores
items.body: Me encantó, la tela es suave y extiende. Hace muy bonita la forma del cuerpo. Read more
items.author: Lucy

items.title: 2.0 out of 5 stars Unfortunately had to return
items.body: The fabric was really nice and not see though. Thick material. The reason I’m giving it two stars is because the folding part at the shoulders did not stay down/ in place , had to keep fixing it every movement. Read more
items.author: Amanda

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Dress is cute, condition is poor.
items.body: The dress is thick material and cute but it arrived with animal hair all over it and gross looking stains or something. I would think they would check the condition of the returns before just sending it right back out. So gross and disappointed! Read more
items.author: Coco

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Dress it up or down
items.body: Wenrine Womens Off The Shoulder Bodycon Sweater Dress (Black, Small): Beautifully well-fitted soft comfortable dress. Perfect for fall and winter. The length will keep you a little bit warmer. The off-the-shoulder is elegant. I'm 5'2" with measurements 29"x26"x36" and the small it fits really well. Simple and sophisticated, dress it up for a formal occasion or down for a less formal occasion. Looks good however you choose. Great find! Read more
items.author: WINNT

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars cute dress, but not on me
items.body: This is one of those dresses that clearly has a “type” and I am apparently not on that vision board. I will say it fit perfectly size wise and the fabric is actually really nice. Thick, not see through, and feels expensive. The off the shoulder fold situation was my enemy. It would not stay down and I had to fix it every time I moved. Unfortunately, I cannot reach my own back because I was blessed with T Rex arms, so that was an adventure. You also have to be pretty comfortable in your body to pull this off. If you wear Spanx and have the patience of a saint, you might love it. I wasn’t wearing Spanx and my confidence was on vacation. It is very warm though, so at least you will be cozy while questioning your outfit decisions. Read more
items.author: Mandi White

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Bodycon Maxi Cocktail Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Bodycon Maxi Cocktail Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Red, Khaki, White, Beige, Red Bean Paste, Black, Coffee, Navy Blue, Grey. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
